      • addAssociatedContexts

        public static void addAssociatedContexts​(BaseEntityUtils beUtils,
                                         HashMap<String,​Object> ctxMap,
                                         String contextAssociationJson,
                                         boolean overwrite)
        This method is used to find any associated contexts. This allows us to provide a default set of context associations that the system can fetch for us in order to reduce code in rules and other areas. Author - Jasper Robison (30/09/2021)
        Parameters:
        beUtils - Standard genny utility
        ctxMap - the context map to add to, and fetch associations from.
        contextAssociationJson - the json instructions for fetching associations.
        overwrite - should the function overwrite any already existing contexts
